TEST test-3
RECEIVE HTTP:GET http://localhost:3000/users/3

EXPECT READ:MYSQL users
USING_SQL """
SELECT `users`.* FROM `users` WHERE `users`.`id` = 3 LIMIT 1
"""
RETURNS {{payloads/mysql_user_single_read_result.yaml}}

RESPOND HTTP:200
WITH {{payloads/user_single_resp.yaml}}
NOISE
  id
  password_digest
  body.created_at
  body.updated_at
